617
00:43:54,880 --> 00:43:57,200
两分钟前是83%
As of two minutes ago, 83%.

618
00:43:59,170 --> 00:44:01,080
赛斯起草了讲话  等我们落地后用
Seth drafted a speech for when we land.

619
00:44:01,660 --> 00:44:03,950
一般来说  邓巴会等你先发表讲话
Normally, Dunbar would wait to give her speech until after yours,

620
00:44:03,950 --> 00:44:05,120
但既然我们在飞机上
but since we're on the plane--

621
00:44:05,120 --> 00:44:07,480
-给她打电话  我让她  -好  先生
- Get her on the phone and I'll concede. - Yes, sir.

622
00:44:10,870 --> 00:44:13,090
看那个乳臭未干的小白脸
Look at that snot-nosed pretty-boy.

623
00:44:13,260 --> 00:44:15,400
他肯定刚学会刮胡子
I'll bet he just learned how to shave.

624
00:44:18,310 --> 00:44:19,330
接邓巴
Get me Dunbar. 

625
00:44:21,320 --> 00:44:23,430
-女士  我真觉得...  -开门
- Ma'am, I really think-- - Open it.

626
00:44:24,280 --> 00:44:26,140
她想一个人待着
She wants to be left alone.

627
00:44:26,140 --> 00:44:27,310
打开门
