630
00:44:54,000 --> 00:44:55,460
你为什么没告诉我
why didn't you tell me?

631
00:44:55,770 --> 00:44:58,750
因为不关你的事
Because it was none of your business.

632
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:02,800
-听我说  -不  别费口舌了
- Just listen to me. - No, don't even bother.

633
00:45:03,010 --> 00:45:06,300
