634
00:45:06,940 --> 00:45:10,730
但也还是一样伤人
But that doesn't make it any less hurtful.

635
00:45:50,820 --> 00:45:53,280
那是为了我还是为了你自己
Is that for me or for yourself?

636
00:45:57,390 --> 00:45:58,400
克莱尔
Claire.

637
00:45:59,840 --> 00:46:00,750
过来
Come here.

638
00:46:04,290 --> 00:46:05,240
过来
Come here. 

639
00:46:08,530 --> 00:46:10,560
你比他强大
